ccowsay
=======
This program displays all of its arguments in a speech bubble.
With your choice of animal/person/thing underneath it. Or in
other words this program is a re-make of the famous Perl
program ``cowsay"

Man Page
--------
Usage:
    The flags should be the first set of arguments.
    ccowsay <flag(s)> Sentence to say

Flags:
    -h or --help    - Displays this help text
    -l or --list    - List all cowfiles
    -c or --cow     - Specify cowfile
    -e or --eyes    - Specify character used for the eyes. Must be ONE character!
    -t or --thought - Thought bubble